comments: [Observable in enhanced video] Barton (DEN) lifts his pivot foot before the start of his dribble.
Dieng (MIN) is not established in a legal guarding position at the time of the contact with Barton (DEN) and his heel is positioned inside the restricted area.
Jokic (DEN) makes contact with Wiggins's (MIN) arm that affects his ability to secure the rebound.
Barton (DEN) makes marginal contact with Wiggins (MIN) on the perimeter that does not affect his SQBR.
Harris (DEN) makes marginal contact with Reynolds (MIN) off ball that does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
At the end of Reynolds' (MIN) drive to the basket, Harris (DEN) reaches in and makes contact with the ball and the part of Reynolds' hand that is considered part of the ball.

RAR shows prior to his gather, Saric (MIN) moves laterally into the path of Millsap (DEN) and initiates contact that affects his SQBR.  Saric never establishes himself in a legal guarding position in Millsap's path.
Dieng (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Murray (DEN) and does not deliver contact.
Murray (DEN) makes marginal contact to the body of Jones (MIN) during the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Barton (DEN) releases from the contact and does not extend his arm into Wiggins (MIN) to create space.
Wiggins (MIN) briefly places an arm around Jokic (DEN) during the pick but immediately slides it off.
Jokic (DEN) and Dieng (MIN) engage and disengage during the rebound.
Barton (DEN) places a hand/arm to the front of Wiggins (MIN) during the drive but the contact is marginal and does not affect his SQBR.
LAR shows Jokic (DEN) makes contact to the wrist of Wiggins (MIN) and the contact causes him to lose control of the ball.
Murray (DEN) releases from the contact with Wiggins (MIN) but does not extend his arm into him to create space.
RLB shows Wiggins (MIN) makes contact with Murray's (DEN) arm and affects his ability to release the pass.
Jones (MIN) commits a take foul on Jokic (DEN).
Barton (DEN) reaches in and makes marginal contact with Wiggins (MIN) that does not affect his SQBR.
Barton (DEN) makes incidental contact to the arm of Wiggins (MIN) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Dieng (MIN) commits a take foul on Millsap (DEN).
Barton (DEN) makes incidental contact with Saric's (MIN) arm during the rebound.
